04:00.741 --> 04:01.575
- Hey. Sexual assault,
secondary trauma.

04:03.577 --> 04:05.579
- Busy night. I have a husband
and wife being worked on.

04:05.579 --> 04:06.814
- [whispering]
Yeah, those are her parents.

04:06.814 --> 04:08.482
- Oh, my God.

04:08.482 --> 04:11.051
- Sophie, Dr. Patel is gonna
take care of you, okay, sweetie?

04:11.051 --> 04:12.453
- Get her in that bay.

04:12.453 --> 04:14.955
- All right, you're gonna be
just fine.

04:14.955 --> 04:16.957
- Lieutenant Benson,
how are the vics?

04:16.957 --> 04:18.125
- Alive.

04:18.125 --> 04:19.460
- Same M.O. as last week?

04:19.460 --> 04:21.329
- Apparently,
looks like we have a bad guy

04:21.329 --> 04:22.730
working your precinct.

04:22.730 --> 04:24.131
I mean, we're gonna run the DNA,
but I--

04:24.131 --> 04:25.733
- You're still short-staffed,
right?

04:25.733 --> 04:27.768
Whatever you need,
just ask.

04:27.768 --> 04:29.637
Vertical patrols,
get last week's sketch out.

04:29.637 --> 04:32.506
- Okay, how about I address
your next roll call?

04:32.506 --> 04:34.342
Also, I'm gonna need to borrow
a couple of detectives

04:34.342 --> 04:36.143
to interview the vics
when they're ready to talk.

04:36.143 --> 04:37.911
- You got it.
- Thank you.

04:37.911 --> 04:40.348
- I need to see
Cynthia and Sophie.

04:40.348 --> 04:42.583
- Doctors are with them,
Mr. Harris.

04:42.583 --> 04:45.118
Right now, just tell us
what you remember.

04:46.620 --> 04:48.522
- It's fuzzy.

04:48.522 --> 04:50.524
I was knocked out.

04:50.524 --> 04:52.159
- Take your time.

04:52.159 --> 04:57.665
- [sighs]
I get home from work late.

04:57.665 --> 05:03.504
He comes out
with a gun to Cynthia's head.

05:03.504 --> 05:05.573
Pistol-whips me.

05:05.573 --> 05:08.942
Makes her tie me up.

05:08.942 --> 05:11.278
Then he rapes her.

05:12.880 --> 05:15.949
- Can you describe him?

05:15.949 --> 05:19.086
- Big, black, late 20s.

05:19.086 --> 05:21.389
- What about his hair?

05:21.389 --> 05:24.191
Anything about the clothes
he was wearing?

05:24.191 --> 05:28.396
- Uh, bit of an afro,
some kind of a team jersey.

05:30.698 --> 05:34.201
- Is this the man you saw?

05:34.201 --> 05:36.770
- Maybe.

05:36.770 --> 05:38.606
That the push-in rapist?

05:39.973 --> 05:42.476
My brother warned me
about him.

05:42.476 --> 05:43.811
- Who's your brother?

05:43.811 --> 05:45.846
- He's on the job,
the one-two.

05:47.748 --> 05:50.584
You haven't caught
this guy yet?

05:50.584 --> 05:52.152
- I didn't see him
in the hallway,

05:52.152 --> 05:54.488
but he was right behind me.
He pushed me inside.

05:54.488 --> 05:56.223
- Did he have a gun?

05:56.223 --> 05:57.491
- Yes.

05:57.491 --> 06:00.694
I gave him my purse,
my PIN number.

06:00.694 --> 06:03.163
I just--I did
whatever he told me to,

06:03.163 --> 06:05.198
but I was worried
about my husband coming home,

06:05.198 --> 06:07.334
that--
[sobs]

06:07.334 --> 06:09.437
I should have screamed.
I should have warned Alec!

06:09.437 --> 06:12.673
- Cynthia,
he could have killed you.

06:12.673 --> 06:14.141
You survived.

06:14.141 --> 06:15.843
Your husband survived.

06:15.843 --> 06:17.745
Your daughter survived.

06:17.745 --> 06:20.448
- Okay.
Okay.

06:20.448 --> 06:22.683
- Excuse me, we need to start
the rape kit now.

06:22.683 --> 06:24.452
- Okay.

06:31.459 --> 06:33.461
- Hey, how are the vics?

06:33.461 --> 06:34.495
- Not great.

06:34.495 --> 06:35.896
- He made the husband watch?

06:35.896 --> 06:37.097
- Yeah.
- Son of a bitch.

06:37.097 --> 06:38.732
Then he rapes
the little girl too?

06:38.732 --> 06:41.034
- Some of our guys
know the husband's brother.

06:41.034 --> 06:43.203
He's good police.

06:43.203 --> 06:44.705
- God help this guy
when we catch him.

06:44.705 --> 06:45.706
- Yeah.

06:45.706 --> 06:46.774
- You get a DNA hit yet?

06:46.774 --> 06:48.108
- I don't think so.

06:48.108 --> 06:49.943
Detective Rollins is
leaning on the M.E.

06:49.943 --> 06:52.245
- Rollins?
Oh, she's sharp.

06:52.245 --> 06:53.847
Yeah, we worked a case
together out in Brooklyn

06:53.847 --> 06:55.749
