Kind of hit it off.

06:55.749 --> 06:57.084
- Oh, did you?

06:57.084 --> 07:00.120
- Yeah.
Maybe I'll just go say hello.

07:02.623 --> 07:03.791
Detective Rollins.

07:07.094 --> 07:09.663
- Doom, how are ya?

07:09.663 --> 07:12.500
- I'm good. I'm good.
Congratulations.

07:12.500 --> 07:15.503
Who's the lucky dad?
Someone I know?

07:15.503 --> 07:16.704
- I don't think so.

07:16.704 --> 07:20.808
- All right, attention.
We got a lot to cover.

07:20.808 --> 07:23.511
Captain Reece.

07:23.511 --> 07:25.012
- You've heard
about our pattern rapist,

07:25.012 --> 07:26.847
so I won't waste
any time.

07:26.847 --> 07:30.518
SVU is here to walk you
through the relevant details.

07:30.518 --> 07:31.852
Lieutenant Benson?

07:31.852 --> 07:33.854
- So last night,
a push-in rape occurred

07:33.854 --> 07:36.123
about three blocks
from the one a week ago.

07:36.123 --> 07:38.792
Perp had a gun
and he assaulted each member

07:38.792 --> 07:41.662
of the family, including
their 12-year-old daughter.

07:41.662 --> 07:45.032
- And yes, the victims are
related to a brother officer.

07:45.032 --> 07:47.067
This is family.

07:47.067 --> 07:49.537
Detective Rollins.

07:49.537 --> 07:51.639
- Look, the first vic
worked up this sketch.

07:51.639 --> 07:52.840
Now, we're still waiting
for the DNA

07:52.840 --> 07:54.542
from last night's attacks,

07:54.542 --> 07:58.145
but one of the vics did give us
details that do match this.

07:58.145 --> 07:59.847
Now, he took
the wife's credit cards,

07:59.847 --> 08:01.815
so we have flagged them.
We've left 'em open.

08:01.815 --> 08:04.752
- Canvass the neighborhood.
Lean on your CIs.

08:04.752 --> 08:07.621
I got no problems
with stop-and-frisk tonight.

08:07.621 --> 08:09.456
He's hit our precinct
twice this week.

08:09.456 --> 08:12.225
He has to have roots here.
Someone knows him.

08:12.225 --> 08:15.295
- Remember, he's armed,
extremely dangerous,

08:15.295 --> 08:16.930
looking at serious time.

08:16.930 --> 08:19.332
- I know it's hot.
Keep your vests on.

08:19.332 --> 08:22.302
Time, distance, cover
are your friends.

08:22.302 --> 08:25.639
I don't care if this scumbag
makes it through the night.

08:25.639 --> 08:28.642
I care if you do.
Understood?

08:28.642 --> 08:29.943
all: Understood.
- Yes, sir.

08:29.943 --> 08:32.112
- All right,
let's hit it.

08:36.917 --> 08:39.787
- Gentlemen, want to slide
over here right quick?

08:39.787 --> 08:42.856
- Nah, nah, man.
Stop-and-frisk is over.

08:42.856 --> 08:45.492
- Stop-and-shut-up isn't.

08:45.492 --> 08:47.327
- You seen this guy?

08:47.327 --> 08:49.496
- Why?
You gonna shoot him?

08:51.364 --> 08:52.866
- Look again.

08:52.866 --> 08:55.168
- I know ten brothers
who look like that.

08:55.168 --> 08:58.205
- Start naming 'em.

08:58.205 --> 09:00.307
- Excuse me, ma'am, would you
mind looking at this photo?

09:00.307 --> 09:01.875
- Why am I being harassed?
I'm just walking.

09:01.875 --> 09:03.010
- Okay, just put a name
to the face

09:03.010 --> 09:04.211
and then we'll move on.

09:04.211 --> 09:05.613
- Am I under arrest?
Otherwise,

09:05.613 --> 09:07.014
I don't have to answer
your questions.

09:07.014 --> 09:09.717
- Okay, Ma'am, he raped
a 12-year-old girl.

09:09.717 --> 09:11.484
You don't want him
on the street.

09:13.787 --> 09:15.422
- Yo, you've seen this guy?
- I don't know him.

09:15.422 --> 09:16.624
- How about you look
at the sketch first,

09:16.624 --> 09:18.025
then answer?

09:18.025 --> 09:19.693
How about you, bro?
You seen this guy?

09:19.693 --> 09:22.062
- He may have been here
about half an hour ago.

09:22.062 --> 09:24.698
He had one of them
throwback jerseys on.

09:24.698 --> 09:26.700
Number 23.

09:26.700 --> 09:28.736
- And you're sure
you haven't seen this man?

09:28.736 --> 09:30.470
- No. I wish
I could help you,

09:30.470 --> 09:32.105
but I've never seen
that man before.

09:32.105 --> 09:33.206
- Thank you, sir.

09:33.206 --> 09:34.374
Well, that was useless.

09:34.374 --> 09:35.442
What are we, 0 for 6?

09:35.442 --> 09:36.877
- Hold on, maybe not.

09:36.877 --> 09:39.079
Rollins just got a hit
on the bank card.

09:39.079 --> 09:40.413
- This the guy?

09:40.413 --> 09:43.450
- Yeah.
I got it right here.

09:46.787 --> 09:48.756
- Okay, how long ago
was this?

09:48.756 --> 09:50.290
- Maybe 15 minutes.

09:50.290 --> 09:51.424
- Hard to see his face.

09:51.424 --> 09:52.826
- You got anything else?

09:52.826 --> 09:56.129
- No, but I see him.
