shoot me.

10:00.300 --> 10:01.468
- He had a gun?

10:01.468 --> 10:03.103
- I saw something
on his right side.

10:03.103 --> 10:04.604
- Lock the neighborhood down.

10:04.604 --> 10:06.774
- Central, form a perimeter
around 131st Street.

10:06.774 --> 10:09.276
Let transit know perp was
last seen 15 minute ago.

10:09.276 --> 10:10.678
- We're on it.
