but he could be trying others.

10:15.282 --> 10:17.317
- You got it.

10:20.420 --> 10:21.822
- Spotted him?

10:21.822 --> 10:23.824
- Yeah, he was in the bodega
15 minutes ago.

10:23.824 --> 10:26.927
- 10-13. Suspect headed south
on Frederick Douglass and 129

10:26.927 --> 10:28.161
toward the projects.

10:28.161 --> 10:30.530
